[DQC.US.0087.9371] The element OperatingLeaseLiabilityNoncurrent with a value of 21,000,000 has been used in the filing but does not appear in the financial statements of the filing. This disclosure should appear in the face financials unless it is included in another account caption. If this is the case either: 1. The element OperatingLeaseLiabilityNoncurrentStatementOfFinancialPositionExtensibleList should be used to identify the account where the Operating Lease liability Noncurrent is included; or 2. The Balance Sheet location axis should be used with two or more account members to identify into which financial statement captions the Operating Lease liability Noncurrent has been apportioned.
Period :2024-12-31 Dimensions : Unit : USD Decimals: -5
Rule Element Id:9371 Rule version: 26.0.9 - zk2532836.htm 19135
